snippet.title: Super Donkey (Rev. A) - SNES Prototype
snippet.description:
Yesterday some big Nintendo leaks happened. This is a prototype of an unknown game that was in the archives. I'm getting Yoshi's Island and Rayman vibes from this honestly.


Super Donkey (Rev. A) (c) 199? Nintendo Co, Ltd.
Emulator: bsnes (libretro)
